pre.code:
library IMMZConfig
using FHIR version '4.0.1'
define "High incidence of TB and/or high leprosy burden": true define "Polio-endemic country with high risk of spread": true /* define "Combined bOPV and IPV Schedule": true define "Sequential IPV-OPV Schedule": true */ /* * Possible Polio dose schemes are 'combined', 'sequential', or 'ipv' */ define "Polio dose scheme": 'combined' define "Country has a high risk of exposure to polio": true define "High Coverage of Polio and Risk of Wild Importation": true
define "In a country where the peak burden of severe Hib disease occurs in young infants":true define "In a setting where the greatest disease morbidity and mortality occur later, or whererate reductions of disease are not fully sustained after the routine use of Hib vaccine": true define "Hib dose scheme": '1p' define "Hepatitis A endemic country": true
define "Japanese Encephalitis dose scheme": 'attenuated' /* define "Country is administering Live recombinant JE antigen":true define "Country is administering Live attentuated JE antigen": true define "Country is administering Inactivated Vero cell-derived JE antigen": true */ define "Country recognizes JE as a health priority": true
/* define "Country is following a 2 dose scheme for Pneumococcal": true define "Country is following a 3 dose scheme for Pneumococcal": true */ define "Pneumococcal dose scheme": '2p+1' define "Country is not highly endemic for Hepatitis A":true define "Country is administering a Live attenuated HAV vaccine": true define "In a setting with a high disease burden and mortality": true
define "Region recommends Meningococcal vaccination": true define "Region recommends Cholera vaccination": true define "Region recommends Typhoid vaccination": true define "Country is administering the TCV vaccine": true define "Country is administering ViPS vaccine": true define "Country is administering an Inactivated HAV vaccine": true define "In a setting where the risk of measles among infants < 9 months of age remains high": false define "Country currently has a measles outbreak": false define "Population is in conflict zones internally displaced populations and refugees": false define "In a setting where there is high transmission of Measles":false define "In a setting where there is low transmission of Measles":false
define "Country has Yellow Fever Endemic": true define "Country recognizes TBE as a priority": true
define "There is a compelling reason to vaccinate infants with Meningococcal between 3 to 9 months old": true define "Country recognizes Varicella an important public health burden": true define "Country recognizes MUMPS reduction as a public health priority": true define "Country is using a 3 dose series ROTA product": true // TODO: //define "bOPV and IPV Schedule": // 'combined' //'sequential';
